quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,Ne eshinyasio shianje nisho eshinyasio eshilulu muno
  15,51,Ne baboolele amakhuwa kabacheni ba Ibrahim
  15,52,"Olwa benjila ewuwe nibaboola mbu; “mulembe” naboola mbu : “toto efwe khubakorerwe.”"
  15,53,Nibaboola mbu; Olaria tawe efwe khukhusubisia Omusiani wa machesi amanji”
  15,54,"Naboola; “Oh! Mumboolelanga kano, nemalile okhukofula, kho ni munjila shina yamumboolelangamwo kano?”"
  15,55,Nibaboola mbu; “Toto efwe khukhuboolela khubwatoto kho sholaba mubalia abafwitsanga omwoyo tawe.”
  15,56,Naboola mbu; “Ne niwina ufwitsanga omwoyo okhurulana nende tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe halali balia abakora?”
  15,57,Naboola; “Mana shiamumbolela shindi nishina enywe Abarumwa
  15,58,Nibaboola mbu; “Efwe khurumilwe khubandu abamabii”
  15,59,Halali balia abaloonda Luti. Toto efwe khwitsa okhuhabina abo boosi
  15,60,Halali omukhasi wuwe khumalile okhulola mbu alaba mubandu balitong’a inyuma
  15,61,Mana Abarumwa olwa boola khubandu ba Luti
  15,62,(Luti) naboola; “Toto enywe muli Abandu balamanyishe tawe.”
  15,63,Nibaboola mbu; “mana efwe khukhureerere kalia kabakholelanga obukanakani” nomulembe
  15,64,"“Ne khukhwitsile khubulaamba, netoto efwe khuboolanga obwatoto.”"
  15,65,"“Kho rula nende Abandu bawo, ebise bilala mubise bieshilo, nawe abalondekhwo, neyesiyesi mwinywe alakalukhanakhwo okhuhenga inyuma tawe, nemutsie wamulomesibungwa"
  15,66,"Nenikhumubusilia likhuwa elo, mbu emisi chiabu chitsa okhutetwa mumabwibwi"
  15,67,Ne Abandu belitokho elo nibetsa nibasangalile
  15,68,(Lut) Naboola mbu; “Toto bano ni abacheni banje khomulafimbia omurwe tawe”
  15,69,"“Ne murie Nyasaye, ne mulafimbia omurwe tawe”"
  15,70,"Nibaboola mbu: “efwe shikhwakhukaniakho (okhurera) Abandu (belwanyi)"
  15,71,"Naboola mbu: “ bano nabakhana banje itse ebahelesie(mubateshie) toto enywe nimuli abakholanga"
  15,72,"Nditsuba khulubaka lulwo, mbu : “abo bali mubumesi bwabu nibanyakhananga eshikhaya.”"
  15,73,Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi
  15,74,"Mana nikhukhola hasi wabu okhuba hekulu, mana nikhubakwisilia ifula ya machina yeliloba lwomumulilo.”"
  15,75,Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubandu baretsanga amakhuwa khushichelo
  15,76,Ne toto tsingongo etso tsili khutsinjila tsiburungwakhwo
  15,77,Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubasuubili
  15,78,Netoto Abandu bomushitsimi bali ababii
  15,79,"Mana nikhubahelesia eshinyasio, ne ebialo bibili bino bili khunjila ili habulafu"
  15,80,Netoto Abandu ba Hijri bayingasia Abarumwa
  15,81,Ne nikhubahelesia abimanyisio biefu nabo nibalabukulamwo oluchendo tawe
  15,82,Ne bakwotanga tsingulu nibakasia tsinzu
  15,83,Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi
  15,84,Mana akabakholanga nikalabakhonyakhwo shiosi shiosi tawe
  15,85,"Ne shikhwalonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio halali khubwatoto, ne toto indukho iliula , kho leshela okhuleshela okhulayi"
  15,86,Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye omuloonji ne niye Omumanyi muno
  15,87,Ne khwakhwelesia tsinyaali saba tsisomungwa ebise nebise nende Ikurani yoluyali
  15,88,"Ne olakhosia tsimoni tsitsio khukalia akakhwahelesia emikanda chindi hakari wabu, nohomba olababelelela tawe. Ne wishilie abasuubili olubaa lulwo. (lwetsimbabaasi)"
  15,89,"Ne boolambu:“ toto esie nesie Omwikanyilisi Omwinoosi.(owahabulafu)"
  15,90,Shingala khweshilia balia (eshinyasio bosi) balia abekaba emikanda (okhwikalila abusalamu)
  15,91,Balia bakhola Ikurani okhuba omubunjikho kwobubeyi
  15,92,Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mbu khulibareeba bosi
  15,93,Khukalia koosi akabakholanga
  15,94,Kho yusia akawalomesibwa ne obe ehale nende Abatsokaasi
  15,95,Toto efwe khukhuyela okhulinda nende abakhubayilanga
  15,96,Balia abatsokasinjia Nyasaye nende Abanyasaye bandi balitsa okhumanya
  15,97,Netoto khwamanya mbu eshilifu shishio shinyoolanga obusiro khukalia akababoolanga
  15,98,"Kho tswenula Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khulwa okhumwitsoomia , ne obe halala nende bamwinamilanga nibasujuda"
  15,99,Ne olaame Nyasaye wuwo okhuula likhuulile eliatoto elo . (lifwa)